ownedComment.body: Step Three Report Consumer (e.g. insurance company) queries by license plate number and can see Reviewed Bad Driver Reports

Step One Moblle App uploads Video and Video Metadata (location, timestamp, etc) to the Report Poster's Account. Report Poster adds Report Description and posts the Unreviewed Bad Driver Report to a Review Queue

Step Two Report Reviewer reviews Unreviewed Bad Driver Reports from the Review Queue. When a Bad Driver Report is verified by at least one independent Report Reviewer, it is added to the Bad Driver Database. It remains in the Review Queue until it has been verified by 3 independent Report Reviewers.
